OL,3,C'For the 97': Hillsborough Law to be
OL,4,Cintroduced by disaster anniversary
OL,6,F"A law for Liverpool, a law for the
OL,7,F97": The Prime Minister vowed to
OL,8,Fdeliver Hillsborough Law in his key
OL,9,Fnote speech at the Labour party
OL,10,Fconference.
OL,12,FA "Hillsborough Law" will be
OL,13,Fintroduced in Parliament before the
OL,14,Fnext anniversary of the football
OL,15,Fstadium tragedy, Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,16,Fconfirmed.
OL,18,FThe Prime Minister told the Labour
OL,19,FParty Conference that he would make a
OL,20,F"law for Liverpool and a law for the
OL,21,F97" victims of the 1989 disaster.
