OL,3,C'For the 97': Hillsborough Law to be
OL,4,Cintroduced by disaster anniversary
OL,6,FCampaigners have been calling for
OL,7,Flegislation to prevent the experiences
OL,8,Fof families of the fans who were
OL,9,Fkilled happening again, and to help
OL,10,Fvictims of other scandals to get
OL,11,Fjustice.
OL,13,FThe Hillsborough Law would introduce a
OL,14,Flegal duty of candour on public
OL,15,Fbodies, with the potential for
OL,16,Fcriminal sanctions for officials or
OL,17,Forganisations which mislead or
OL,18,Fobstruct investigations.
