OL,3,C'For the 97': Hillsborough Law to be
OL,4,Cintroduced by disaster anniversary
OL,6,FSir Keir said that it was also a law
OL,7,Ffor the sub-postmasters of the Horizon
OL,8,Fscandal, victims of infected blood,
OL,9,FWindrush, Grenfell Tower and "all the
OL,10,Fcountless injustices over the years
OL,11,Fsuffered by working people at the
OL,12,Fhands of those who were supposed to
OL,13,Fserve them."
OL,15,F"Truth and justice concealed behind
OL,16,Fclosed ranks of the state, and
OL,17,Fconference, this is the meaning of
OL,18,Fclause one, because today I can
OL,19,Fconfirm that the duty of candour will
OL,20,Fapply to public authorities and public
OL,21,Fservants.
