OL,3,C'For the 97': Hillsborough Law to be
OL,4,Cintroduced by disaster anniversary
OL,6,F"The Bill will include criminal
OL,7,Fsanctions and that the Hillsborough
OL,8,Flaw will be introduced to Parliament
OL,9,Fbefore the next anniversary in April,"
OL,10,Fhe said.
OL,12,FThe change sees the Government taking
OL,13,Fforward recommendations made by Bishop
OL,14,FJames Jones in his 2017 report into
OL,15,Fthe experience of the Hillsborough
OL,16,Ffamilies in the years following the
OL,17,Fcrush which resulted in the death of
OL,18,FLiverpool supporters at the stadium in
OL,19,FSheffield.
