OL,3,C'For the 97': Hillsborough Law to be
OL,4,Cintroduced by disaster anniversary
OL,6,FA spokeswoman for Hillsborough Law
OL,7,FNow, says: "We are heartened by such a
OL,8,Fpositive message from Sir Keir today,
OL,9,Fparticularly the commitment that his
OL,10,FHillsborough Law will deliver
OL,11,Faccountability across all public
OL,12,Fbodies.
OL,14,F"Let today be the start of a period of
OL,15,Ftrue transparency and accountability
OL,16,Fin public life, where bluster is
OL,17,Fconfined to the annals of the past and
OL,18,Fcandour is the new way of working.
