OL,3,C'For the 97': Hillsborough Law to be
OL,4,Cintroduced by disaster anniversary
OL,6,F"Sir Keir is right that this law is
OL,7,Fabout all of those who have suffered
OL,8,Fat the hands of those who were
OL,9,Fsupposed to serve them and it's to all
OL,10,Fthose who have fought for justice that
OL,11,Fthis truly groundbreaking legislation
OL,12,Freally belongs.
OL,14,F"The devil will be in the detail, but
OL,15,Fwe will work with the government to
OL,16,Fmake sure the Hillsborough Law
OL,17,Fdelivers for all."
