OL,3,C'For the 97': Hillsborough Law to be
OL,4,Cintroduced by disaster anniversary
OL,6,FAlongside the promised law, the
OL,7,FGovernment has begun the process of
OL,8,Frecruiting the first independent
OL,9,Fpublic advocate (IPA).
OL,11,FThe IPA will be sent to the scene of
OL,12,Fany future public disaster, playing a
OL,13,Fpivotal role in ensuring victims,
OL,14,Fsurvivors, and bereaved families get
OL,15,Fthe information and support they need.
OL,17,FThe advocate is expected to be in post
OL,18,Fby next summer and will inform victims
OL,19,Fabout sources of support, advice and
OL,20,Fservices available to them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
