OL,3,C'For the 97': Hillsborough Law to be
OL,4,Cintroduced by disaster anniversary
OL,6,FThe role will also help victims
OL,7,Funderstand actions taken by public
OL,8,Fauthorities in relation to the
OL,9,Fincident, including how to navigate
OL,10,Finquiries, inquests and other formal
OL,11,Fprocesses that may follow a public
OL,12,Fdisaster.
OL,14,FThe IPA will also communicate with
OL,15,Fpublic authorities on behalf of
OL,16,Fvictims.
OL,18,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,19,FPolitics? Tom, Robert and Anushka dig
OL,20,Finto the biggest issues dominating the
OL,21,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
